dcws

This is a small data-focused package to make easier use of the DataHaven Community Wellbeing Survey. It contains the data extracted from crosstabs from the 2015, 2018, 2020, 2021, 2022, and 2024 survey waves. 2020 and 2022 are statewide only.

Installation

You can install the development version of dcws from GitHub with:

# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("CT-Data-Haven/dcws")
